<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">6月25日上午，江西软件职业技术大学党委理论学习中心组学习（扩大）会议在行政楼一楼会议室召开。会议由党委书记、督导专员江延湖主持。全体校领导、党群部门负责人、党总支部书记(直属党支部书记)参加会议。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><a href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-07-02%2021%3A32%3A13575d13ec1598bbb514a8203ed2c6675.jpg?Expires=2035287135&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=P7X5qSaFVPFQAHg%2BZTRPzBv7FBw%3D" data-fancybox="gallery" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; transition: all 0.3s ease-in 0s;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-07-02%2021%3A32%3A13575d13ec1598bbb514a8203ed2c6675.jpg?Expires=2035287135&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=P7X5qSaFVPFQAHg%2BZTRPzBv7FBw%3D" class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); width: 600px; height: 400px;" width="600" height="400" border="0" vspace="0" title="" alt=""/></a></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">党委书记、督导专员江延湖传达《关于转发〈关于认真学习领会习近平总书记关于全面加强党的纪律建设的重要论述 扎实开展党纪学习教育的通知〉》并领学《习近平关于全面加强党的纪律建设论述摘编》。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">党委副书记、执行校长范红铭领学《关于认真学习贯彻习近平总书记重要讲话精神 推动党纪学习教育走深走实的通知》《庄兆林同志在省委党纪学习教育工作专班第二次会议上的讲话》《庄兆林同志在省委党纪学习教育工作专班第三次会议上的讲话》《关于支持各民主党派、无党派人士开展党纪学习教育的工作方案》。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">而后，招就处处长、保卫处处长和软件工程学院党总支部书记就加强党的纪律建设，结合部门工作实际谈谈招就处工作开展情况、存在的问题及下一步打算作交流发言。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">江延湖强调，党纪学习教育是一项长期而艰巨的任务。大家要认真学习《习近平关于加强党的纪律建设论述摘编》书中的重要论述，认真贯彻落实党在新时期的系列路线、方针和政策，以求真务实的工作作风；同时，要把党纪学习教育与实际工作结合起来，统筹安排、一体推进，聚焦重点、强化落实，进一步在学纪中明方向、在知纪中守规矩、在明纪中修品德、在守纪中善作为，用有力举措把党纪学习教育引向深入。</span></p><p><br/></p>